commitResults.messageTitle: Renamed Chatbot to Friendly Bot. Implemented skeletal version of greet and exit.
Improved skeletal version: Echoes commands entered by user and exits upon "bye"
Added abiity for Friendly Bot to store tasks and return to user when requested.
Added the ability to mark tasks as done. Added the ability to mark tasks as undone. Catches exceptions where given task index is out of range or when given task index is not an integer.

Added support for tracking three types of tasks: todos, deadlines, events Added new Classes for ToDo, Deadline and Event. Added toString method for Task. Added 3 new commands for todo deadline and event to create these task types.
Added Automated Text UI Testing using the input/ouput redirection technique.
FriendlyBot now correctly deals with incorrect inputs.
Added support for deleting tasks in the list. Changed the data structure used for storing tasks from using Array to ArrayList.
Added JavaDocs for the following files.
